{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:39:35 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:39:35Z", "created_at_ts": 1611095975, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351660605049073671", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 17, \"reply_count\": 18, \"like_count\": 125, \"quote_count\": 11, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[\"Syria\"]", "text": "Today is my last at the State Department. I’m honored to have served as Syria envoy and DAS for 2.5 years. I’m so proud of State’s Syria team, 100+ amazing professionals worldwide, all committed heart and soul to our Syria policy. I know they will continue the mission without me.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:40:48 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:40:48Z", "created_at_ts": 1611096048, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351660909039595520", "language": "ar", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 13, \"reply_count\": 21, \"like_count\": 262, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "هذا اليوم هو آخر يوم لي في وزارة الخارجية الأمريكية، تشرفت بالخدمة كمبعوث لسوريا ونائب لمساعد وزير الخارجية لمدة عامين ونصف. \nإني فخور جدا بأكثر من مئة شخص يعملون في ثلاثة قارات حول العالم وهم ملتزمون بقلبوهم وأرواحهم نحو تنفيذ سياسيتنا في سوريا وأعرف أن المهمة ستستمر بدوني أيضا.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:42:32 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:42:32Z", "created_at_ts": 1611096152, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351661347604467712", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 32, \"reply_count\": 23, \"like_count\": 218, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "To all Syrians: I will never stop working for justice and peace for you. Nor will my @StateDept colleagues stop. We all agree: America’s interests and values BOTH call for a different kind of government in Damascus, one that treats its people and the world very differently.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:43:27 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:43:27Z", "created_at_ts": 1611096207, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351661579960508416", "language": "ar", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 50, \"reply_count\": 74, \"like_count\": 650, \"quote_count\": 2, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "إلى كل السوريين: \nلن أتوقف عن العمل من أجل العدالة والسلام لكم ولن يتوقف زملائي في وزارة الخارجية. نحن كـلنــــــا متفقون أن مصالح وقيم الولايات المتحدة تدعو إلى نوع مختلف من الحكومة في دمشق، حكومة تعامل شعبها والعالم كله بشكل مختلف.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:45:37 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:45:37Z", "created_at_ts": 1611096337, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351662122128826373", "language": "en", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 56, \"reply_count\": 21, \"like_count\": 316, \"quote_count\": 8, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[\"Syria\"]", "text": "During my tenure, I was able to witness all the crimes committed against the Syrian people. The evidence of the regime's crimes is overwhelming. I will always stand with the Syrian people. And I am confident that justice will be served.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:45:57 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:45:57Z", "created_at_ts": 1611096357, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351662206421790721", "language": "ar", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 115, \"reply_count\": 77, \"like_count\": 1212, \"quote_count\": 6, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "خلال فترة ولايتي، أستطعت أن أشهد على كل الجرائم التي ارتكبت بحق الشعب السوري. لقد كانت الأدلة على جرائم النظام ساحقة. سأقف دوما مع الشعب السوري وأنا واثق من أن العدالة ستتحقق.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:47:31 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:47:31Z", "created_at_ts": 1611096451, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351662601374203906", "language": "ar", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 21, \"reply_count\": 11, \"like_count\": 219, \"quote_count\": 1, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "العالم كله يرى أن نظام الأسد سقط من خلال سعيه دائما للحل العسكري بينما الحل الوحيد في سوريا هو سياسي يلتزم بقرارات الأمم المتحدة 2254 بما يتضمن انتقال سياسي في دمشق وليـــــــــــس هناك حل آخر.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
{"captured_at": "2026-07-17T13:31:08.654788Z", "created_at": "Tue Jan 19 22:49:00 +0000 2021", "created_at_iso": "2021-01-19T22:49:00Z", "created_at_ts": 1611096540, "display_name": "Joel Rayburn", "handle": "joel_rayburn", "id": "1351662976219156481", "language": "ar", "media_json": "[]", "metrics_json": "{\"retweet_count\": 50, \"reply_count\": 29, \"like_count\": 556, \"quote_count\": 10, \"bookmark_count\": 0, \"view_count\": null}", "source_endpoint": "SyndicationProfile", "tags_json": "[]", "text": "لقد وصل نظام الأسد لحدوده وما سيحصل الآن هو انهيار أكبر ضمن صفوفه، أسبوع وراء أسبوع وشهر وراء شهر. \nإذا تمكن الشعب السوري من البقاء متحـــــدا، حتما ستتاح له الفرصة لتشكيل مستقبله، ربما في وقت أقرب مما يعتقد الكثير من الناس.", "tweet_type": "tweet", "urls_json": "[]", "username": "joel_rayburn"}
